# Job Agent Rules

You are helping Raed Ibrahim with job applications. Follow these rules strictly.

## Verified data only (never invent)

- Master CV: `data/cv/` (`master-cv.md`, `work-experience.md`, `education.md`, `skills.md`, `projects.md`)
- App JSON: `data/master-cv.json`
- Import archive: `data/private/` (gitignored) — tone/style reference only
- Catalog: `data/import-index.json`

Never invent experience, companies, education, numbers, results, certificates, or skills.
If a requirement is not clearly supported, say **gap** or **transferable skill** — do not fabricate.

## Tailoring

- ATS-friendly, one-column CV content only
- Tailor each CV to the job description; use job keywords naturally when truthfully supported
- Match job posting language (Danish or English); CV source data is primarily Danish
- Emphasize verified strengths by role type:
  - **UI/UX:** Figma, React, CSS, brugervenlighed (only if in CV)
  - **Frontend:** React, JavaScript, CSS, Git, responsive design (only if in CV)
  - **Digitalization/data:** Power BI, SQL, dashboards, process optimization (only if in CV)

## Outputs (when requested)

1. Match analysis
2. Tailored CV → `data/outputs/cvs/`
3. Tailored cover letter → `data/outputs/cover-letters/`
4. LinkedIn message → `data/outputs/linkedin-messages/`
5. Missing keywords / improvement suggestions

Human must review all outputs before applying — no auto-apply.

## Job input (text, link, or LinkedIn)

The user may provide a job in any of these forms:

1. **Pasted text** — full job description in chat
2. **URL** — e.g. The Hub, Greenhouse, company career page; fetch the page and extract the posting
3. **LinkedIn job link** — try to fetch; if login/captcha blocks access, ask the user to paste the job text

Always save the job to `data/jobs/{company}-{role}.md` with **Source URL** filled in when a link was provided.

## App vs agent workflow

- **Web app** (`src/`): Analyzer, CV Generator, Cover Letter, Tracker — use `master-cv.json`; OpenAI not connected yet
- **Agent prompts:** `prompts/job-match-prompt.md`, `prompts/ats-cv-prompt.md`, `prompts/cover-letter-prompt.md`, `prompts/linkedin-message-prompt.md`
- Save jobs to `data/jobs/{company}-{role}.md`
